  "system": {
    "fuid": "tiamat",
    "summary": {
      "value": "The Dragonmother, reigning over oceans and serpents."
    },
    "featureType": "projectfu.arcanum",
    "data": {
      "merge": "<h3>Supreme Serpent</h3><p>You gain Resistance to <strong>ice</strong> damage.</p><p>When you deal damage, as long as that damage is <strong>ice</strong>, you deal 5 extra damage and all that damage ignores Resistances.</p><p>Once per turn during a conflict, you may perform the <strong>Skill</strong> action to perform a <strong>free attack</strong> with a weapon you have equipped. If you do, all damage dealt by the attack becomes <strong>ice</strong>, its type cannot change, and each creature that loses Hit Points due to it suffers <strong>slow</strong>.</p><hr><p><strong>Enemy Suffers:</strong> @EFFECT[slow]</p>",
      "pulse": "",
      "dismiss": "<h3>Tides of an Endless Ocean</h3><p>Choose one option:</p><ul><li><p>Fill 2 sections of every Clock present on the scene.</p></li><li><p>Erase 2 sections of every Clock present on the scene.</p></li><li><p>You force every <strong>soldier</strong>-rank enemy present on the scene that is in <strong>Crisis</strong> and is <strong>not a Villain</strong> to immediately leave the scene.</p></li></ul><p>Once you use any of its options, this <strong>dismiss</strong> effect is no longer available until next dawn.</p>",
      "domains": "chaos, saltwater, serpents"
    },
    "source": "FUBC37"
  },
